'''A demonstration program for GCGB and GCB.
'''--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
'''This program is a demonstration of a Flashing LED.
'''The LED array must be attached via appropiate resistors.
'''********************************************************************************

' ----- Configuration
#CHIP 16f1459, 48
'must for usb Bootloader
#OPTION Bootloader 0x200
'Tells compiler not to set config bits
#OPTION NoConfig
'All variables must be declared!
#OPTION Explicit

#DEFINE timerWait 500

' ----- Define Hardware settings
Dir PORTa Out


'----- Variables
'  Dim PWMCOUNT, PWMLEVEL as Byte   ' to do

' ----- Main body of program commences here.
Main:


PulseOut PORTa.5, timerWait ms
Wait timerWait ms

Goto Main
End
